tribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"LogicHunt\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6887:\"<p>Joomla is a free and open-source content management system (CMS) for publishing web content. It is built on a model–view–controller web application framework that can be used independently of the CMS.</p>
<p>There are many free Joomla extensions in the Joomla gallery for the betterment of your site. But it is always a challenge to find and combine the right extensions for your Joomla project. On this website you can preview and download my free extensions. I try to create simple, easy to use extensions and keep them up to date. From all free Joomla extensions I have made a great list of it.</p>
<h3>1. Akeeba Backup:</h3>
<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />
<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>
<p>Akeeba Backup Core is the most widely used open-source backup component for the Joomla! CMS. Its mission is simple: create a site backup that can be restored on any Joomla!-capable server, making it ideal not only for backups but also for site transfers or even deploying sites to your clients&#8217; servers. Akeeba Backup creates a full backup of your site in a single archive.</p>
<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/access-a-security/site-security/akeeba-backup</p>
<h3>2. AcyMailing Starter:</h3>
<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />
<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>
<p>AcyMailing is a reliable Newsletter and email marketing extension for Joomla.<br />
AcyMailing enables you to efficiently manage an unlimited number of subscribers, organize them into mailing lists, send personalized newsletters.</p>
<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/marketing/newsletter/acymailing-starter</p>
<h3>3. JEvents:</h3>
<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />
<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>
<p>JEvents is a well known and Loved Events Calendar / Management solution for Joomla. JEvents provides a full events and calendar solution for your Joomla! site. Showing your events in listings or as a visual monthly calendar view, create complex repeats patterns, import and export your events with a couple of clicks, offer a feed with your latest events&#8230; And also with more than 40 languages translated, we are likely to have a translation for your website.</p>
<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/calendars-a-events/events/jevents</p>
<h3>4. HikaShop:</h3>
<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />
<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>
<p>HikaShop is an E-Commerce extension for Joomla 1.5, 2.5 and 3.x. It is built for simplicity and flexibility.<br />
HikaShop also has a wide range of marketing tools, but also powerful statistics displayable on your HikaShop dashboard to help you manage your store. It provides advanced taxes, zones, languages and currencies management for worldwide sales as well as advanced customization capabilities of your online shop in order to meet your website ecommerce needs.</p>
<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/e-commerce/shopping-cart/hikashop</p>
<h3>5. Admin Tools:</h3>
<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />
<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>
<p>Admin Tools is a true Swiss Army knife for your site. Our freely available Admin Tools Core will detect, notify you about new Joomla! releases, fix your files&#8217; and directories&#8217; permissions, protect your administrator directory with a password, change your database prefix, migrate links pointing to your old domain on-the-fly and perform database maintenance, all with a single click.</p>
<p>http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/access-a-security/site-security/admin-tools</p>
<h3>6. Event Gallery:</h3>
<p><strong>Includes: Component, Plugin</strong><br />
<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>
<p>Event Gallery is an easy to use gallery component. It supports adaptive, flexible and responsive layouts and provides a unique way of presenting images. If presenting is not enough enable the cart! Let users browse through your images and buy them.</p>
<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/photos-a-images/galleries/event-gallery</p>
<h3>7. Creative Contact Form:</h3>
<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />
<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>
<p>Creative Contact Form is a powerful contact form generator with amazing visual effects. You will be surprised by count of all the possible features! Over 67,000+ sites are already using Creative Contact Form.</p>
<p>http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/contacts-and-feedback/contact-forms/creative-contact-form</p>
<h3>8. GMapFP : Google Map:</h3>
<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />
<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>
<p>Thanks to GMapFP, you can use Google Maps very easily in your Joomla site. This component is natively compatible with Joomla and is available French and English. It&#8217;s compatible with JoomFish, XMAP, JComments and Joomla search module. GMapFP is translated in many languages.</p>
<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/maps-a-weather/maps-a-locations/gmapfp-google-map</p>
<h3>9. All Video Share:</h3>
<p><strong>Includes: Component, Module, Plugin</strong><br />
<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>
<p>A complete and flexible video share solution for Joomla with a wide range of features. Support all major Joomla versions, Support responsive templates, Handle variety of Media formats that flash can handle such as flv, mp4, 3g2, 3gp, aac, f4b, f4p, f4v, m4a, m4v, mov(h.264), sdp, vp6. HTML5 fallback. Color the skin on your Own.<br />
Flexible options to add Videos either by simply providing Video URL (or) using UPLOAD method. Youtube API to play Youtube videos.</p>
<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/multimedia/multimedia-players/allvideoshare</p>
<h3>10. Tag Meta:</h3>
<p><strong>Includes: Component, Plugin</strong><br />
<strong>Compatibility: 3</strong></p>
<p>Tag Meta allows to efficiently manage all site&#8217;s meta information. With Tag Meta, as example, it is possible to set the tag &#8216;title&#8217; or the meta tags (e.g. from the most common &#8216;description&#8217;, &#8216;keywords&#8217;, &#8216;robots&#8217;, as well as the recently &#8216;content rights&#8217; and &#8216;external reference&#8217;) or link &#8216;canonical&#8217; on any page, just specifying the URL or a part of it. This provides a swiss army knife to improve site positioning in SEO optimization. But Tag Meta also supports regular expressions in the matching rules and this allows to match a group of URLs with a single rule. In this way it is possible to manage metadata from a single control panel.</p>
<p>Details: http://extensions.joomla.org/extensions/extension/site-management/seo-a-metadata/tag-meta</p>
